[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "临近清晨的崇福街很安静，几乎所有的店铺都关了门，只留下闪烁的霓虹灯，把巷子照得斑驳陆离。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "带着寒气的风呼呼掠过，吹得头顶上挂着的一串串红灯笼胡乱摇晃着。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "玫色长发的少女向前快步走着，鞋子踏在石板路上，却没有一点声音。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "茉莉安幽潮",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_girl005_01",
        "zh_CN": "这么晚了，你准备去哪里？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_01",
        "zh_CN": "啊！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "茉莉安冷冷的声音从巷口的屋檐上传来，在这样昏暗的夜色中，她就像个没有实体的幽灵。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "下一瞬，她无声无息地站在了瑟茜面前，彻底封死了去路。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "瑟茜果断回头，却在看清道路另一头的我和安卡希雅后，瞳孔骤然收缩。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_02",
        "zh_CN": "主……主管……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_03",
        "zh_CN": "我是打算……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "打算去布置那些气味和声音对吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "之前你提到过，你的天启者能力是精神系。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "从游客们的表现上看，不是单纯的幻觉迷惑。再加上你需要借助声音、气味作为媒介……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "所以，是“心理暗示”，对吗？你给崇福街的所有人种下了“在大洪水到来前，必须要留在这里”的暗示？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在我揭穿瑟茜的手段之后，瑟茜脸上却浮现出意外的欣慰，甚至如释重负地笑了笑。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_04",
        "zh_CN": "太好了，我就知道主管不会被影响的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_05",
        "zh_CN": "我很抱歉一直瞒着你们，但你们会来崇福街，确实在我的计划之外。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_06",
        "zh_CN": "昨天见到你们时，我以为心理暗示已经种下了，所以不敢灌输与其相悖的事实，担心让你们的精神崩溃。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_07",
        "zh_CN": "不过好在大家都没事呢。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她的语气很轻松，轻松到让人感到一股寒意，从脊背攀爬而上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "为什么？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_08",
        "zh_CN": "为什么？当然是为了抓住苏菲啊。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "瑟茜推了推眼镜，语气中带着一丝困惑。看我没有回应，她还是温和又耐心地解释了起来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_09",
        "zh_CN": "您忘了神谕是怎么说的了吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_10",
        "zh_CN": "苏菲不只是要洗涤罪恶，她还想接引虔信者的灵魂。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_11",
        "zh_CN": "要是按照大迁徙计划，人真的都撤往阿尔斯特内陆了，罗森兰还怎么作为苏菲的目标？我们又怎么抓住她？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你的意思是，崇福街居民都是你的饵？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_12",
        "zh_CN": "嗯！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她点了点头，动作干脆利落。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_13",
        "zh_CN": "想让苏菲按照她的原计划行动，至少也要做到这种程度。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_14",
        "zh_CN": "本来想等心理暗示到更深层状态时再告诉您的……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_15",
        "zh_CN": "主管，我想向您证明，您可以依赖、相信我，像以前一样。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "少女玫色的长发在风中轻轻飘动，发丝不断掠过她红扑扑的脸颊，和带着微微笑意的嘴角。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "可要是我们没能阻止苏菲，洪水真的来了怎么办？你打算让这些人送死吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "感受到我的情绪后，瑟茜皱了皱眉，脸上闪过一丝犹疑。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_16",
        "zh_CN": "我……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_17",
        "zh_CN": "我也有为她们想过的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_18",
        "zh_CN": "留在这里的人，大部分都上了年纪，要么就是想去瓦尔哈拉的朝圣者。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_19",
        "zh_CN": "就算洪水来了，她们也逃不过这一劫，或者说……她们根本不想逃。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_20",
        "zh_CN": "是我的力量，才让怀旧展变得梦幻，就像真的回到了那个时候一样。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_21",
        "zh_CN": "没有大洪水、没有降临团、没有泰坦，她们享受一段快乐时光的同时，又帮了我们，这不好吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "从头到尾，瑟茜的语气都很平静，眼神清澈而坦然，甚至没有一丝愧疚。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "解开她们的心理暗示。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_22",
        "zh_CN": "诶？为什么？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "瑟茜身体僵住了，声音也有些发颤，仿佛不敢相信自己听到的话。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "想要抓住苏菲，我们有很多方法可以选择。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但你选择了最不该选的那一种。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她们是活生生的人，有为自己决定的权利，不是你达成目的的工具。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_23",
        "zh_CN": "可是……可是我只是想帮您……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我不需要这样的帮助，瑟茜，靠无谓牺牲换来的胜利根本就毫无意义。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在我说完之后，瑟茜紧紧咬住嘴唇，很快那上面就出现了一抹鲜红。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她品尝着嘴里的铁锈味，努力克制着内心翻涌的痛苦，眼神从期待变成了失望，又从失望变成了绝望。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_24",
        "zh_CN": "又是毫无意义……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_25",
        "zh_CN": "也就是说，我做什么，都得不到您的注视对吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我不是这个意思。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "瑟茜缓缓抬起了头，印象中，她很少这样直视我的目光。大多数时候，她总是低着头，或者把视线落在别处。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "可现在，那双青色的眸子直直地看着我，里面燃烧着愤怒的火焰。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 58,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "六年间的情绪好像在这一刻找到了出口，即将猛烈地爆发出来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 59,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_28",
        "zh_CN": "为了替您寻找苏菲，我能想到的也只有这种卑劣的办法。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 60,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_29",
        "zh_CN": "我只是，只是想让我们回到以前那种关系，这很难吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 61,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_30",
        "zh_CN": "不要什么拯救世界，不要什么伟大使命，您为什么非要成为一个我够不着的人呢！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 62,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "瑟茜，你冷静一下。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 63,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_31",
        "zh_CN": "我很冷静！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 64,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她紧紧抓着胸前的衣服，每说一个字都用尽全力、咬牙切齿。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 65,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "大颗大颗的泪珠滚落，少女的身体忽地失去平衡，跌坐在地上，像一个被遗弃的布娃娃，所有的生气都从身体里流走了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 66,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_32",
        "zh_CN": "但主管您……还是离我越来越远了……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 67,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "瑟茜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc35ep7_sexi_33",
        "zh_CN": "为什么啊……呜呜……呜……到底为什么会这样啊……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 68,
        "Flag": "",
